Package org.emoncms

Interface Feed

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HibernateFeed, HttpFeed, RedisFeed, SqlFeed
    public interface Feed
    The Feed interface is used to communicate with an emoncms webserver and handle feed specific actions. An feed instance can be used to
    • Retrieve the latest and historical data.
    • Get configuration information.
